acceptPropertyUpdate

protected void acceptPropertyUpdate(java.lang.String category,
                                    java.lang.String tradingPropertyKey)
Accept events for a property being updated. For simplicity, the group cache is cleared allowing future get calls to repopulate.

Parameters:
category - The category the group was in.
tradingPropertyKey - The key for the group that was updated.

acceptPropertyRemove

protected void acceptPropertyRemove(java.lang.String category,
                                    java.lang.String tradingPropertyKey)
Accept events for a property being removed. This means that a set of category definitions has been totally removed. This is bizare, but go ahead and remove them from the cache.

Parameters:
category - The category the group was in.
tradingPropertyKey - The key for the group that was removed.
